description: Powerful winds cause dramatic scenes as flights are cancelled and homes are left without power.
title: In pictures: Storm Ciara batters north-western Europe
title_page: In pictures: Storm Ciara batters north-western Europe - BBC News
maintext: Storm Ciara - known as Sabine in Germany and Switzerland and Elsa in Norway - has caused hundreds of flights to be grounded and rail services cancelled in Germany, France, Belgium, the Netherlands and the UK.
